2011-07-08T08:43:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/acard-technology-june-sales-fall-21-80-table-3126-tt.html
ACARD TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 21.80% to NT$20,163,000 from NT$25,785,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             20,163           25,785    
YOY%             -21.80%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            107,535          144,728    
YOY%             -25.70% 
=================================================================
 